        </div>
        <div id="platform-chatgpt" class="platform-info">
            <h3><i class="fab fa-openai"></i> ChatGPT Search Architecture</h3>
            <p><strong>Core Technology:</strong> GPT-4 with web browsing, code interpreter, and DALL-E integration</p>
            <p><strong>Search Method:</strong> Bing API integration with custom ranking algorithms and real-time web access</p>
            <p><strong>Unique Features:</strong> Multi-modal responses, code execution, conversation memory, plugin ecosystem</p>
        </div>

        <div id="platform-perplexity" class="platform-info">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-atom"></i> Perplexity Search Architecture</h3>
            <p><strong>Core Technology:</strong> Multiple LLMs (Claude, GPT-4, Llama) with specialized search infrastructure</p>
            <p><strong>Search Method:</strong> Real-time web indexing with source citation and fact-checking mechanisms</p>
            <p><strong>Unique Features:</strong> Source transparency, academic search mode, real-time information synthesis</p>
        </div>

        <div id="platform-claude" class="platform-info">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Claude Search Architecture</h3>
            <p><strong>Core Technology:</strong> Anthropic's Claude with constitutional AI training</p>
            <p><strong>Search Method:</strong> Contextual reasoning with web access through integrated tools</p>
            <p><strong>Unique Features:</strong> Constitutional AI safety, long-context processing, analytical depth</p>
        </div>

        <div id="platform-gemini" class="platform-info">
            <h3><i class="fab fa-google"></i> Gemini Search Architecture</h3>
            <p><strong>Core Technology:</strong> Google's Gemini Ultra with deep Google services integration</p>
            <p><strong>Search Method:</strong> Google Search integration with Knowledge Graph and real-time data</p>
            <p><strong>Unique Features:</strong> Native Google ecosystem integration, multimodal understanding, real-time data access</p>
        </div>

