            <!-- Query Input & Preprocessing -->
            <div class="process-card" data-step="1">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-keyboard"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-title">Query Input & Preprocessing</div>
                    <div class="card-expand"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-summary">
                        Initial processing of user queries including normalization, language detection, and basic intent classification.
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Technical Components</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Text Normalization:</strong> Unicode standardization, case folding, punctuation handling</li>
                                    <li><strong>Language Detection:</strong> Statistical models (n-gram analysis) and neural language identification</li>
                                    <li><strong>Tokenization:</strong> BPE (Byte-Pair Encoding), WordPiece, or SentencePiece tokenization</li>
                                    <li><strong>Query Classification:</strong> Intent classification using transformer-based classifiers</li>
                                    <li><strong>Spam Detection:</strong> Pattern recognition to filter malicious or irrelevant queries</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i> Platform Implementations</h4>
                            <div class="platform-specific">
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>ChatGPT:</strong> GPT tokenizer with conversation context preservation
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Perplexity:</strong> Multi-language preprocessing with search-specific optimization
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Claude:</strong> Constitutional AI filtering integrated into preprocessing
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Gemini:</strong> Google's multilingual preprocessing with Knowledge Graph integration
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="optimization-tip">
                            <h5>Optimization Strategy: Query Formulation</h5>
                            <p>Structure queries using natural language patterns. Use specific, descriptive terms and include context. For technical queries, include relevant terminology and specify desired output format.</p>
                        </div>

