                            <h4><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Technical Components</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Intent Classification:</strong> Multi-class classification (informational, navigational, transactional)</li>
                                    <li><strong>Named Entity Recognition (NER):</strong> Identification of people, places, organizations, dates</li>
                                    <li><strong>Semantic Analysis:</strong> Understanding relationships and context using transformer models</li>
                                    <li><strong>Query Complexity Assessment:</strong> Determining single-hop vs. multi-hop reasoning requirements</li>
                                    <li><strong>Temporal Analysis:</strong> Detection of time-sensitive information needs</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
