                        <div class="optimization-tip">
                            <h5>Optimization Strategy: Intent Clarity</h5>
                            <p>Be explicit about your intent. Use action verbs (explain, compare, analyze, list). Include context about your audience or use case to help AI systems provide appropriately targeted responses.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-industry"></i> Industry Examples</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Legal:</strong> "Explain contract law implications" â†’ Requires authoritative, detailed analysis</li>
                                    <li><strong>Technology:</strong> "Compare cloud providers for startups" â†’ Comparative analysis with business context</li>
