            <!-- Embedding Generation -->
            <div class="process-card" data-step="3">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-vector-square"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-title">Embedding Generation</div>
                    <div class="card-expand"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-summary">
                        Conversion of text into high-dimensional vector representations for semantic similarity matching and retrieval.
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Technical Components</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Transformer Encoders:</strong> BERT, RoBERTa, E5, or custom embedding models</li>
                                    <li><strong>Vector Dimensions:</strong> Typically 384-1536 dimensions for semantic representation</li>
                                    <li><strong>Normalization:</strong> L2 normalization for cosine similarity computation</li>
                                    <li><strong>Multimodal Embeddings:</strong> CLIP-like models for text-image joint representations</li>
                                    <li><strong>Domain Adaptation:</strong> Fine-tuned embeddings for specific knowledge domains</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i> Platform Implementations</h4>
                            <div class="platform-specific">
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>ChatGPT:</strong> OpenAI text-embedding-3 models with 1536 dimensions
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Perplexity:</strong> Custom embeddings optimized for search relevance
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Claude:</strong> Anthropic's embedding models with safety alignment
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Gemini:</strong> PaLM-based embeddings with multimodal capabilities
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="optimization-tip">
                            <h5>Optimization Strategy: Semantic Richness</h5>
                            <p>Include related terms and synonyms in your content. Use semantic clustering of related concepts. Structure content with clear topic hierarchies to improve embedding quality and retrieval relevance.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-industry"></i> Industry Examples</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Medical:</strong> Symptom descriptions â†’ Medical condition embeddings with ICD-10 mapping</li>
                                    <li><strong>Legal:</strong> Case descriptions â†’ Legal precedent embeddings with citation networks</li>
                                    <li><strong>Academic:</strong> Research abstracts â†’ Paper embeddings with field-specific terminology</li>
                                    <li><strong>Business:</strong> Company descriptions â†’ Industry embeddings with competitive analysis</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Knowledge Retrieval (RAG Pipeline) -->
            <div class="process-card" data-step="4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-title">Knowledge Retrieval (RAG Pipeline)</div>
                    <div class="card-expand"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-summary">
                        Retrieval-Augmented Generation system that searches knowledge bases and web sources for relevant information.
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Technical Components</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Vector Databases:</strong> Pinecone, Weaviate, Milvus, or Chroma for embedding storage</li>
                                    <li><strong>Hybrid Search:</strong> Combination of dense (vector) and sparse (BM25) retrieval</li>
                                    <li><strong>Multi-Stage Retrieval:</strong> Initial retrieval followed by re-ranking and filtering</li>
                                    <li><strong>Web Crawling:</strong> Real-time or cached web content retrieval with freshness scoring</li>
                                    <li><strong>Knowledge Graphs:</strong> Structured knowledge representation (Wikidata, proprietary KGs)</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i> Platform Implementations</h4>
                            <div class="platform-specific">
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>ChatGPT:</strong> Bing API + proprietary knowledge base with real-time web access
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Perplexity:</strong> Multi-source aggregation with real-time indexing and source verification
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Claude:</strong> Curated knowledge sources with safety-filtered retrieval
                                </div>
                                <div class="platform-item">
                                    <strong>Gemini:</strong> Google Search + Knowledge Graph + Scholar integration
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="optimization-tip">
                            <h5>Optimization Strategy: Source Visibility</h5>
                            <p>Ensure your content is crawlable and well-structured. Use schema markup, clear headings, and semantic HTML. Create comprehensive, authoritative content that establishes topical authority in your domain.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tech-section">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-industry"></i> Industry Examples</h4>
                            <div class="tech-list">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> PubMed abstracts + medical databases â†’ Evidence-based health information</li>
