                                    <li><strong>Approximate Nearest Neighbors (ANN):</strong> HNSW, IVF, or LSH algorithms for fast search</li>
                                    <li><strong>Similarity Metrics:</strong> Cosine similarity, Euclidean distance, or dot product</li>
                                    <li><strong>Index Optimization:</strong> Quantization, pruning, and compression for scale</li>
                                    <li><strong>Multi-Vector Search:</strong> Query expansion and multiple embedding strategies</li>
                                    <li><strong>Filtering & Metadata:</strong> Post-retrieval filtering based on freshness, authority, relevance</li>
                                </ul>
